OL,3,CWife of dad killed by falling branch
OL,4,Cvows his death 'won't be for nothing'
OL,6,FFiona Hall and her son Sam spoke to
OL,7,Four correspondent Andy Bonner.
OL,9,FA woman whose husband was killed by a
OL,10,Ffalling tree branch while out walking
OL,11,Fhis dog is vowing that his death
OL,12,F"won't be for nothing."
OL,14,FChristopher Hall, 48, died from
OL,15,Fmultiple injuries in the incident at a
OL,16,Fpublic park near his home in Wilmslow,
OL,17,FCheshire, in August 2020.
