OL,6,FFiona Hall has launched a petition
OL,7,Fcalling for mandatory tree maintenance
OL,8,Fin public places.
OL,10,FShe told ITV Granada Reports that the
OL,11,Fincident had "obliterated everything."
OL,13,FShe said: "It just robbed him of his
OL,14,Flife in a heartbeat, simply walking
OL,15,Fyour dog in the most avoidable wholly
OL,16,Favoidable situation known to man."
OL,18,FMrs Hall said the tree that killed her
OL,19,Fhusband was 130 years old.
