OL,6,FThe HSE said the council, which
OL,7,Fmanaged the park, did not have a
OL,8,Fformal, overarching strategy to manage
OL,9,Fthe risks from trees in public areas.
OL,11,FIt added that the authority's grounds
OL,12,Fservices contractor, Ansa
OL,13,FEnvironmental Services Ltd, also had
OL,14,Fno robust tree management policy.
