OL,6,FCouncillor David Jefferay, chair of
OL,7,FCheshire East Council's environment
OL,8,Fand communities committee, said: "My
OL,9,Fthoughts and those of the council
OL,10,Fremain with the family and other loved
OL,11,Fones of Mr Hall - I also understand
OL,12,Fthe impact this has had on the wider
OL,13,Flocal community.
OL,15,F"Since this tragic incident, we have
OL,16,Fimplemented a number of improvements
OL,17,Fin line with our adopted tree
OL,18,Fmanagement strategy. Our priority is
OL,19,Fto ensure the safety of everyone who
OL,20,Fvisits and enjoys our green spaces."
