OL,6,FFiona's petition has attracted more
OL,7,Fthan 34,000 signatures and the issue
OL,8,Fis also due to be raised in parliament.
OL,10,FShe said: "You can't stop trees
OL,11,Ffalling through storms or lightning,
OL,12,Fthat's a given.
OL,14,F"We know that it's very rare, but we
OL,15,Fmust have something in place that is
OL,16,Fjust the basic fundamentals of
OL,17,Fchecking, and a whole roadmap of
OL,18,Fchecking trees properly, particularly
OL,19,Fstarting with the old ones."
